        ],
        "targetSubtopic": "Active Participle",
        "targetTopic": "Active Participle",
        "enclosingTopic": "Present tense",
        "enclosingSubtopic": "Present tense"
       },
       {
        "text": " is sometimes called the “present tense” (or לְשׁוֹן הוֹוֶה ",
